00:35:26,480 --> 00:35:27,970
This only proves

566
00:35:28,000 --> 00:35:30,200
that Yun Hongshen has ties to the CBIS,

567
00:35:30,560 --> 00:35:32,890
and nothing to do with the Communist Party.

568
00:35:33,390 --> 00:35:34,160
I suspect

569
00:35:34,190 --> 00:35:36,700
that Zhang Xiancheng knew he wouldn't survive,

570
00:35:37,000 --> 00:35:38,120
but he had to pass on

571
00:35:38,150 --> 00:35:40,120
the mission details for coming to Changsha.

572
00:35:40,160 --> 00:35:42,080
So he chose Yun Hongshen, the person closest to Yang Ziming,

573
00:35:42,100 --> 00:35:43,790
to act as a messenger.

574
00:35:44,430 --> 00:35:46,550
Anyway, no matter what he said, Yun Hongshen wouldn't have understood,

575
00:35:46,810 --> 00:35:48,000
but he could be certain

576
00:35:48,040 --> 00:35:50,490
that once Yang Ziming knew the situation,

577
00:35:50,510 --> 00:35:52,350
he would ask Yun Hongshen about it,

578
00:35:52,380 --> 00:35:54,030
thus achieving his goal.

579
00:35:54,710 --> 00:35:55,260
Chief,

580
00:35:55,300 --> 00:35:57,180
based on all the current information,

581
00:35:57,200 --> 00:35:59,440
it's highly likely that Yun Hongshen

582
00:35:59,470 --> 00:36:01,070
was simply caught up in this by chance.

583
00:36:01,330 --> 00:36:03,740
He has nothing to do with Zhang Xiancheng's mission in Changsha

584
00:36:03,760 --> 00:36:06,210
or Yang Ziming.

585
00:36:06,600 --> 00:36:08,770
And the notion of him being a Communist is completely unfounded.

586
00:36:09,520 --> 00:36:11,700
The newspaper clipping found at the Yun family's house

587
00:36:11,730 --> 00:36:14,220
was likely planted to frame him.

588
00:36:14,340 --> 00:36:16,860
The death of Jingyu really makes this clear.

589
00:36:29,360 --> 00:36:30,680
Young Master, please eat.

590
00:36:33,190 --> 00:36:34,460
Young Master, don't worry.

591
00:36:34,940 --> 00:36:36,390
We'll keep looking for the people for you.

592
00:36:37,190 --> 00:36:38,100
But I'm worried

593
00:36:38,910 --> 00:36:39,950
that after we startled them this time,

594
00:36:40,190 --> 00:36:40,870
they won't

595
00:36:40,870 --> 00:36:42,420
hide in Bai Qingkui's place anymore.

596
00:36:42,620 --> 00:36:43,270
So,

597
00:36:44,020 --> 00:36:45,570
we'll need to put in more effort.

598
00:36:46,050 --> 00:36:47,860
As long as they haven't disappeared into thin air,

599
00:36:47,880 --> 00:36:49,040
we'll definitely find them.

600
00:36:49,320 --> 00:36:51,680
After all, this is still our Changsha territory.

601
00:36:52,530 --> 00:36:53,230
Young Master.

602
00:36:53,400 --> 00:36:55,950
Where do you think they might hide this time?

603
00:36:56,300 --> 00:36:57,770
I have no clue at all.

604
00:36:58,800 --> 00:37:00,190
Let's look further away.

605
00:37:01,010 --> 00:37:02,890
Now they are surrounded on all sides.

606
00:37:03,100 --> 00:37:04,430
Not only are we looking for them,

607
00:37:04,450 --> 00:37:05,970
but the NBIS people are also looking for them.

608
00:37:06,630 --> 00:37:08,300
They can't hide in the city.

609
00:37:08,840 --> 00:37:09,750
The more remote

610
00:37:09,920 --> 00:37:11,660
and unnoticed the place is,

611
00:37:12,080 --> 00:37:13,210
the more suitable it is for them.

612
00:37:14,770 --> 00:37:15,990
Let's try our luck.

613
00:37:16,450 --> 00:37:17,250
-Alright.
-Alright.

614
00:37:17,990 --> 00:37:18,550
Let's eat.

615
00:37:41,430 --> 00:37:43,150
He's an incredible agent.

616
00:37:43,800 --> 00:37:45,410
As an opponent, I really respect him.

617
00:37:46,000 --> 00:37:47,930
I believe the package he swore to protect

618
00:37:47,950 --> 00:37:48,960
was also for the anti-Japanese war effort.

619
00:37:50,850 --> 00:37:52,860
He's a hero to this country.

620
00:37:54,060 --> 00:37:55,750
He shouldn't have been treated this way.

621
00:37:56,690 --> 00:37:59,010
But the only thing I can do for him is this.

622
00:38:00,980 --> 00:38:01,690
Thank you.

623
00:38:03,250 --> 00:38:04,090
He'll like

624
00:38:04,920 --> 00:38:06,010
this place.

625
00:38:08,230 --> 00:38:09,740
He likes scenic spots.

626
00:38:11,810 --> 00:38:13,030
You're still too young.

627
00:38:14,070 --> 00:38:16,390
Some things you're still too emotionally attached to.

628
00:38:16,990 --> 00:38:18,270
You care that he's your relative,

629
00:38:18,290 --> 00:38:19,660
and you can't bring yourself to report him,

630
00:38:20,210 --> 00:38:22,200
so you've ended up in this situation.

631
00:38:24,100 --> 00:38:25,780
But he's not like that to you.

632
00:38:26,870 --> 00:38:27,520
No.

633
00:38:29,920 --> 00:38:31,230
He wouldn't shoot me.

634
00:38:33,070 --> 00:38:34,160
A person like him

635
00:38:36,760 --> 00:38:37,630
is both terrifying

636
00:38:38,740 --> 00:38:39,570
and admirable.

637
00:38:51,660 --> 00:38:52,810
Tell me,

638
00:38:53,260 --> 00:38:54,980
how did you get Ling Han to meet you?

639
00:38:55,650 --> 00:38:56,690
He has an operative,

640
00:38:56,950 --> 00:38:57,950
code name “Onitetsu.”

641
00:38:58,440 --> 00:38:59,960
I found Ling Han through her.

642
00:38:59,990 --> 00:39:01,250
Is this Onitetsu Mi Lan?

643
00:39:05,270 --> 00:39:07,310
Yeming really went to great lengths for you.

644
00:39:08,070 --> 00:39:09,070
She found out Mi Lan's real reason

645
00:39:09,100 --> 00:39:10,660
for siding with the Japanese,

646
00:39:10,980 --> 00:39:12,100
but she didn't uncover

647
00:39:12,120 --> 00:39:14,440
the evidence of the connection between Mi Lan and Ling Han.

648
00:39:15,000 --> 00:39:16,590
So my suspicion of you and Ling Han

649
00:39:16,620 --> 00:39:17,410
is the same.

650
00:39:17,760 --> 00:39:19,850
How can you prove what you're saying is true?

651
00:39:21,220 --> 00:39:22,670
I will definitely prove it to you.

652
00:39:24,130 --> 00:39:26,000
I will never let Ling Han go.

653
00:39:30,040 --> 00:39:31,290
If you don't have evidence,

654
00:39:31,670 --> 00:39:33,040
then it's just speculation.

655
00:39:33,620 --> 00:39:34,900
Ling Han has also made significant contributions

656
00:39:34,930 --> 00:39:36,480
to our KMT.

657
00:39:36,680 --> 00:39:37,790
When you deal with a person like him,

658
00:39:37,820 --> 00:39:39,480
if you don't have concrete evidence,

659
00:39:39,690 --> 00:39:41,340
you'll only bring trouble upon yourself.

660
00:39:41,740 --> 00:39:42,710
In our line of work,

661
00:39:44,330 --> 00:39:45,890
we can't always rely on evidence.

662
00:39:46,960 --> 00:39:47,800
Many times,

663
00:39:48,730 --> 00:39:49,690
we have to rely on deduction.

664
00:39:52,260 --> 00:39:53,720
That's why I said you are too young.

665
00:39:54,510 --> 00:39:56,200
Yun Hongshen, I understand your abilities,

666
00:39:56,680 --> 00:39:58,080
and I know your thoughts.

667
00:39:58,710 --> 00:40:00,990
But this is no longer just your business.

668
00:40:01,400 --> 00:40:03,410
It concerns the honor of the KMT's elites,

669
00:40:03,670 --> 00:40:04,600
and it also concerns the safety

670
00:40:04,620 --> 00:40:06,180
of our entire Hunan Station.

671
00:40:06,590 --> 00:40:08,230
So now you must tell me everything

672
00:40:08,260 --> 00:40:09,060
you know.

673
00:40:09,430 --> 00:40:10,780
Then why do you suspect him?

674
00:40:12,570 --> 00:40:14,160
You keep talking about evidence.

675
00:40:14,390 --> 00:40:15,520
After all these years of handling cases,

676
00:40:16,510 --> 00:40:17,730
have you always relied on evidence?

677
00:40:23,270 --> 00:40:24,490
I really admire you,

678
00:40:25,030 --> 00:40:26,180
but I want to tell you

679
00:40:26,640 --> 00:40:28,870
that people like us,

680
00:40:29,630 --> 00:40:31,150
when we're in the middle of the situation,

681
00:40:31,170 --> 00:40:32,320
sometimes we don't see things as clearly.

682
00:40:32,930 --> 00:40:34,450
Why have I been openly and covertly

683
00:40:34,680 --> 00:40:35,520
protecting you?

684
00:40:35,640 --> 00:40:37,680
It's to make you believe in me.

685
00:40:40,060 --> 00:40:41,420
When I captured the Viscount,

686
00:40:42,190 --> 00:40:43,720
I unexpectedly uncovered a family letter.

687
00:40:44,570 --> 00:40:46,180
A Japanese spy with the code name Kunwu

688
00:40:46,200 --> 00:40:47,240
had entrusted him to send it back to Japan.

689
00:40:48,270 --> 00:40:49,510
Kunwu is in Changsha.

690
00:40:50,030 --> 00:40:51,520
I suspect Ling Han is Kunwu.

691
00:40:52,000 --> 00:40:53,090
He's been lurking in China

692
00:40:53,120 --> 00:40:54,360
for at least ten years,

693
00:40:54,700 --> 00:40:56,660
maybe even longer than Zhang Hua or Zong Fang.

694
00:40:58,780 --> 00:41:00,570
Is there anything else besides this family letter?

695
00:41:01,170 --> 00:41:01,800
No.

696
00:41:02,240 --> 00:41:03,190
Can this family letter

697
00:41:03,230 --> 00:41:05,320
prove that Ling Han is Kunwu?

698
00:41:05,590 --> 00:41:06,290
No.

699
00:41:07,970 --> 00:41:08,980
Recently, I have been investigating

700
00:41:08,990 --> 00:41:10,140
Ling Han extensively.

701
00:41:10,220 --> 00:41:12,060
I've found many suspicious points about him.

702
00:41:13,440 --> 00:41:15,450
Ling Han is someone who acts very meticulously.

703
00:41:16,190 --> 00:41:17,580
I just don't have evidence for now to prove

704
00:41:17,610 --> 00:41:18,660
that Ling Han is Kunwu.

705
00:41:19,080 --> 00:41:21,050
But I firmly believe Ling Han must be Kunwu.

706
00:41:21,630 --> 00:41:22,200
Chief,

707
00:41:22,430 --> 00:41:23,950
I suggest we arrest Ling Han immediately.

708
00:41:24,030 --> 00:41:24,830
No.

709
00:41:24,850 --> 00:41:25,390
Why not?

710
00:41:25,410 --> 00:41:27,490
Ling Han was personally recommended by Director Dai,

711
00:41:28,000 --> 00:41:29,320
and he holds him in high regard.

712
00:41:29,580 --> 00:41:30,510
Just because of that,

713
00:41:31,500 --> 00:41:32,230
we're going to let a Japanese spy

714
00:41:32,250 --> 00:41:34,170
who has infiltrated so deeply

715
00:41:34,310 --> 00:41:35,750
continue to stab at the heart of our organization?

716
00:41:36,260 --> 00:41:37,300
The longer he remains undercover,

717
00:41:37,360 --> 00:41:38,490
the more secrets he knows.

718
00:41:38,520 --> 00:41:40,640
This will lead to increasingly severe consequences.

719
00:41:46,310 --> 00:41:48,560
This matter is not as simple as you think.

720
00:41:48,880 --> 00:41:50,790
If Ling Han is indeed Kunwu,

721
00:41:50,830 --> 00:41:52,480
then Director Dai will inevitably be implicated.

722
00:41:53,480 --> 00:41:55,810
At that point, the entire NBIS will be in turmoil.

723
00:41:56,450 --> 00:41:57,530
Then what do you intend to do?

724
00:41:58,200 --> 00:41:59,350
Are you saying

725
00:42:00,430 --> 00:42:01,690
that to protect Director Dai,

726
00:42:02,550 --> 00:42:03,830
we should allow Ling Han to maintain

727
00:42:03,860 --> 00:42:04,950
his elite image for the KMT?

728
00:42:04,970 --> 00:42:06,340
Don't talk nonsense with me.

729
00:42:06,530 --> 00:42:08,610
You are fully aware of the stakes involved here.

730
00:42:22,270 --> 00:42:23,510
You can investigate,

731
00:42:24,120 --> 00:42:25,370
but don't make too much noise.

732
00:42:26,010 --> 00:42:27,400
I will find a solution that addresses both sides

733
00:42:27,440 --> 00:42:28,970
in the shortest possible time.

734
00:42:29,270 --> 00:42:31,150
If Ling Han is indeed Kunwu,

735
00:42:31,760 --> 00:42:33,140
I will not let him go.
